{"tid":683450,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人想做國家主席？","createTime":"2018-05-29T16:58:23.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-30T05:44:23.000Z","uid":162406,"like":1,"dislike":22,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"07fc64e0f3ed810984c08e831711d252c1f32bbb","tid":683450,"uid":162406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T16:58:23.000Z","msg":"如果有一個人可以入去共產黨做鬼，之後上位做到一啲話到事嘅人，一路上 上到做國家主席，<br />\n奪權之後就改革，拉哂班共匪食屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁就好啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果有一個咁嘅人就好了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果..有生之年可以親眼目睹中共滅亡就死而無憾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7461e843561a9ffda4ad8d8b91e962f51336567f","tid":683450,"uid":67332,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T17:00:16.000Z","msg":"你唔好話入中共住，你改變到黑警先講喇"},{"pid":"43c7e17826097bfba3eb921cf6ca68dbc0a18cff","tid":683450,"uid":162406,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"7461e843561a9ffda4ad8d8b91e962f51336567f","tid":683450,"uid":67332,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T17:00:16.000Z","msg":"你唔好話入中共住，你改變到黑警先講喇"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T17:06:43.000Z","msg":"改變到個呀頭 咪改變到啲工具，又唔見之前咁多人咁憎警察<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6c10293665610ea180db3e8cc35ba94af679dce","tid":683450,"uid":13914,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T17:08:16.000Z","msg":"萬里死咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2218e57f2941a44867d273e3bb0c0d7b8db70f17","tid":683450,"uid":140738,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T17:17:10.000Z","msg":"潮文召喚"},{"pid":"75047a420acb79f5124002ba3c744568cbb2a833","tid":683450,"uid":20867,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T17:20:22.000Z","msg":"四、五千話多唔多。。。"},{"pid":"9378274b823510b5c